<div id="outline-container-org050c12c" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org050c12c">obsidian</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org050c12c">
<p>
C-c d - open daily 
C-c o - follow link at point
C-c b - follow backlinks
C-c n - open new note
C-c j - jump to an existing note
</p>
